50|$|New Direction was {{established}} in 2010 and draws its inspiration from the 2009 Prague Declaration, from which the Alliance of <b>European</b> <b>Conservatives</b> and Reformists (AECR) and the <b>European</b> <b>Conservatives</b> and Reformists <b>group</b> (ECR) in the European Parliament were founded. As of October 2016, the AECR {{is known as the}} Alliance of Conservatives and Reformists in Europe (ACRE).|$|R
